ainer\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Day 1-4: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/greece\/santorini\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Santorini<\/a><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Begin at one of the most famous Greek Islands: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/greece\/santorini\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Santorini<\/a>! Santorini is known for its white and blue villages built on top of cliffs overlooking the sea. It&#x2019;s also famous worldwide for incredible sunsets, which can be seen from many panoramic viewpoints all over the island. Nothing beats watching the sky burst into color over the sea; an unforgettable moment on your Greek island hopping trip.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04092403\/Greek-island-hopping-1-617x810.jpg\" alt=\"Greek island hopping santorini\"><\/noscript><img width=\"257\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Greek island hopping santorini\" data-id=\"62250\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04092403\/Greek-island-hopping-1.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=62250\" class=\"wp-image-62250 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 617px) 100vw, 617px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04092403\/Greek-island-hopping-1-617x810.jpg 617w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04092403\/Greek-island-hopping-1-457x600.jpg 457w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04092403\/Greek-island-hopping-1-257x338.jpg 257w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/04092403\/Greek-island-hopping-1-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07