 <div class=\"product__content-title\">Milos Inn<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-to-milos\"><strong>Getting <\/strong>to Milos<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Ferry:<\/strong> From Santorini, you can take a high-speed ferry to Milos in just two hours. During peak season (May-September), ferries leave twice a day. During the winter, this goes down to about 7 times a week. The average price is around 45 EUR for the high-speed ferry, but it&#x2019;s cheaper if you choose the slow boat.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ferryhopper.com\/en\/?aff_uid=slthr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get your ferry tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04133001\/Greek-island-hopping-34-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"62353\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04133001\/Greek-island-hopping-34.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=62353\" class=\"wp-image-62353 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-src