ary. It offers a good balance between relaxing on beautiful beaches and enjoying the buzzing nightlife. However, you don&#x2019;t have to be a party animal to enjoy Mykonos. There are still many quiet corners of the island that are perfect for a romantic getaway or unwind after a Greek island-hopping adventure! Particularly in the north of the island, you&#x2019;ll find remote beaches like Panormos. These beaches have crystal clear water and a cooling breeze.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Greek island hopping mykonos\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Greek island hopping mykonos\" data-id=\"62291\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=62291\" class=\"wp-image-62291 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095045\/Greek-island-hopping-20-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\