r a bit more, as this is a popular vacation option.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/osom-mykonos\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/05090110\/osom-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Osom Resort\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/05090110\/osom-450x300.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Osom Resort<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/khamsa-suites-mykonos\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/05090102\/khamsa-30x23.jpeg\" alt=\"KHAMSA suites\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/05090102\/khamsa-450x338.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">KHAMSA suites<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-getting-to-mykonos\"><strong>Getting <\/strong>to Mykonos<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Ferry:<\/strong> From Milos, you can take a high-speed ferry in just under 3 hours to Mykonos. The high-speed option price averages between 40-60 EUR per person.&#xA0;In the winter months, the ferry services between the two islands are normally suspended. During this time, you&#x2019;ll need to change boats at Santorini.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ferryhopper.com\/en\/?aff_uid=slthr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get your ferry tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>By Plane:<\/strong> In peak season, you can also fly between Santorini and Mykonos. Consider changing your Greece itinerary if you&#x2019;d prefer to fly; however, the ferries are a perfect option! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Leaving Greece?<\/strong> If you&#x2019;re heading home from Mykonos, there are plenty of domestic leaving daily to the main hub of Athens and a few international flights to cities like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/paris-city-trip-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Paris<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/amsterdam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Amsterdam<\/a>. Additionally, in the summer months, there are many options for flights to other big cities in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Europe<\/a>.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22.jpg\" alt=\"Greek island hopping\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"304\" alt=\"Greek island hopping\" class=\"wp-image-62296 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-800x540.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-1080x728.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-450x304.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-267x180.jpg 267w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-768x518.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-1024x691.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-1440x971.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095927\/Greek-island-hopping-22-600x405.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"htt