              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23.jpg\" alt=\"island hopping greece\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"island hopping greece\" class=\"wp-image-62298 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04095937\/Greek-island-hopping-23.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-paros\">Paros<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Paros is a livelier alternative to Naxos. By day, visitors can relax in its beautiful secluded coves, and by night there are lots of luxurious cocktail bars and restaurants to choose from. There are also beautiful towns to explore, with boutiques that make it a haven for shopping. If you head inland, you&#x2019;ll discover some ancient villages that have been beautifully preserved.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04131205\/Greek-island-hopping-26-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"Greek island hopping paros\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Greek island hopping paros\" data-id=\"62333\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04131205\/Greek-island-hopping-26.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=62333\" class=\"wp-image-62333 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-conten