n<p>Greek island hopping is very popular among travelers, and there&#x2019;s no better way to explore the beauty of this incredible country. Especially in the summer months, exploring the island&#x2019;s beaches is the perfect way to relax and cool off! During this time, it&#x2019;s super easy to go between the islands via ferry or car ferries if you are by car and most trips take just over 2 hours.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ferryhopper.com\/en\/?aff_uid=slthr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ferryhopper<\/a> is a great search tool to use to check out ferry itineraries, compare prices, and book your tickets. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ferryhopper.com\/en\/?aff_uid=slthr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get your ferry tickets here<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-greece\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">book a rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04134058\/Greek-island-hopping-36.jpg\" alt=\"Greek island hopping ferry\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Greek island hopping ferry\" class=\"wp-image-62359 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/04134058\/Greek-island-hopping-36.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.co